com.phunware.location.manager

Class PwSlLocationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.senionlab.slutilities.service.SLServiceManager
      • com.phunware.location.manager.PwSlLocationManager

  • public class PwSlLocationManager
extends com.senionlab.slutilities.service.SLServiceManager
    The PwSlLocationManager class defines the interface for configuring the delivery of Senion Lab (SL) location-related events to your application. You use an instance of this class to establish the parameters that determine when location events should be delivered and to start and stop the actual delivery of those events.
